OL,3,CHow you could be eligible for #200 to
OL,4,Chelp with heating bills
OL,6,FPeople in Wales struggling to afford
OL,7,Fheating bills due to rising fuel
OL,8,Fprices caused by the conflict in the
OL,9,FMiddle East could be able to access
OL,10,F#200 of support.
OL,12,FThe Welsh Government says anyone on
OL,13,Flow incomes who use heating oil or
OL,14,Fliquid petroleum gas (LPG) will be
OL,15,Feligible for the one-off payment if
OL,16,Fthey are on the Council Tax Reduction
OL,17,FScheme.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/8
