OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1774976749
OL,3,CHow you could be eligible for #200 to
OL,4,Chelp with heating bills
OL,6,FIt comes after the cost of oil rose to
OL,7,Fmore than $112 a barrel after the US
OL,8,Fand Israel launched strikes on Iran
OL,9,Fmore than a month ago.
OL,11,FThe UK Government announced earlier in
OL,12,FMarch that #3.8 million would be
OL,13,Fallocated to Wales to support those
OL,14,Fhaving difficulties in keeping up with
OL,15,Ftheir heating costs.
OL,17,FThose eligible will be invited by
OL,18,Ftheir local authorities to apply and
OL,19,Fwill need to confirm their bank
OL,20,Fdetails with the money being paid
OL,21,Fdirectly into their accounts.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1774976749
OL,3,CHow you could be eligible for #200 to
OL,4,Chelp with heating bills
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government says people will
OL,7,Fhave six months from when the scheme
OL,8,Fwas launched to claim the money.
OL,10,FIt adds that those in severe financial
OL,11,Fhardship who do not qualify can apply
OL,12,Fto the Discretionary Assistance Fund
OL,13,Fwith the maximum award for heating oil
OL,14,Fnow at #750.
OL,16,FPeople can apply twice over the year
OL,17,Ffor this fund, with applications being
OL,18,Fmade through local authorities as well
OL,19,Fas Citizens Advice.
OL,21,FSupport services
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
