OL,3,CHow you could be eligible for #200 to
OL,4,Chelp with heating bills
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government's Cabinet
OL,7,FSecretary for Social Justice, Jane
OL,8,FHutt, said: "The cost of living
OL,9,Fcontinues to put pressure on many
OL,10,Fhouseholds across Wales, and the
OL,11,Fconflict in the Middle East is driving
OL,12,Fup prices, adding to the anxiety many
OL,13,Fpeople already feel about paying their
OL,14,Fbills and heating their homes.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1774976749
OL,3,CHow you could be eligible for #200 to
OL,4,Chelp with heating bills
OL,6,F"Supporting people through these
OL,7,Fpressures is a priority for us and we
OL,8,Fare doing all we can for those who
OL,9,Fneed it most. Today's announcements
OL,10,Fwill provide immediate extra help for
OL,11,Fthose in greatest need, and build on
OL,12,Fthe significant support we have
OL,13,Falready put in place."
OL,15,FIn response to the support announced
OL,16,Fby the Labour government, a
OL,17,Fspokesperson for Plaid Cymru says the
OL,18,Fnews of support will be welcomed by
OL,19,Fhouseholds across Wales but thousands
OL,20,Fwill be ineligible due to the "narrow
OL,21,Fnature of this support."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
