OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1774976749
OL,3,CHow you could be eligible for #200 to
OL,4,Chelp with heating bills
OL,6,F"The Welsh Government must now work to
OL,7,Fensure that any and all eligible
OL,8,Fhouseholds are made aware of the
OL,9,Favailable payment, and encouraged to
OL,10,Ftake advantage of the much-needed
OL,11,Fscheme. The UK Government must
OL,12,Furgently outline what broader support
OL,13,Fit will make available to households
OL,14,Fand business ahead of the Autumn."
OL,16,FHowever, Reform Wales Leader, Dan
OL,17,FThomas says "Labour, just like the
OL,18,FConservatives, have undermined our
OL,19,Fenergy security with net zero madness.
OL,26,@vD@bO]yD@MOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1774976749
OL,3,CHow you could be eligible for #200 to
OL,4,Chelp with heating bills
OL,6,F"Reform has a plan to cut bills and
OL,7,Fcut fuel duty to ease the pressure on
OL,8,Fworking families."
OL,10,FFor the Welsh Conservatives, they say
OL,11,F"this one-off payment will only go so
OL,12,Ffar for families already under
OL,13,Fpressure, and it is limited to those
OL,14,Fon benefits, doing nothing for many
OL,15,Fhard-working households who are
OL,16,Fstruggling but do not qualify for
OL,17,Fsupport.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@RO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/8
