OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1774976749
OL,3,CHow you could be eligible for #200 to
OL,4,Chelp with heating bills
OL,6,F"The Welsh Government should be
OL,7,Fsupporting everyone facing rising
OL,8,Fenergy costs, not just a narrow group,
OL,9,Fand they could do that by
OL,10,Freconsidering the planned increase in
OL,11,Ffuel duty that will place further
OL,12,Fpressure on families.
OL,14,F"That's why the UK Conservatives have
OL,15,Fset out an enhanced Cheap Power Plan
OL,16,Fto cut energy bills by #200 and
OL,17,Fprovide broader, lasting support for
OL,18,Fhouseholds across the UK"
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/8
